    <div class="container text-center" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <span class="pre-head">The Clinical Reality</span>
      <h2>Traditional Talk Therapy Isn't Enough for Complex Trauma.</h2>
      <p class="lead">As a therapist, you know the feeling. You sit across from a client who is profoundly dysregulated, trapped in a freeze response, or looping in trauma narratives. Top-down cognitive approaches hit a wall.</p>
    </div>
